UpdateStakedTokenBalance_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── when caller not Bob
│  └── it should revert
└── when caller Bob
   ├── when user share balance zero
   │  └── it should revert
   └── when user share balance not zero
      ├── when wstETH transfer amount zero
      │  └── it should revert
      └── when wstETH transfer amount not zero
         ├── it should decrease sender wstETH balance
         ├── it should increase recipient wstETH balance
         └── it should emit a {TransferStakedTokens} event
